#. <section class="sutta" id="sn23.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn23.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyamāravagga"
msgstr "2. About Māra (2nd)"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 15. Dukkhasutta → dukkha 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn23.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Dukkhasutta"
msgstr "15. Suffering"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn23.15:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn23.15:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā rādho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Seated to one side, Venerable Rādha said to the Buddha:"

#. </p><p class="added">
msgctxt "sn23.15:1.3"
msgid "“‘dukkhaṃ, dukkhan’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘suffering’."

msgctxt "sn23.15:1.4"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho, bhante, dukkhan”ti?"
msgstr "What is suffering?”"

#. </p><p class="added">
msgctxt "sn23.15:1.5"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ kho, rādha, dukkhaṃ, vedanā dukkhā, saññā dukkhā, saṅkhārā dukkhā, viññāṇaṃ dukkhaṃ."
msgstr "“Rādha, form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness are suffering."

msgctxt "sn23.15:1.6"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "Seeing this …"

msgctxt "sn23.15:1.7"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānātī”ti."
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.15:1.8"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
